Thus below in l. 601 qnid nunc agimus? and Ι. 604 iam dimitto arem-stunt? answers are certainly expected and actually given. So And. 315 adeone ad eum? Adel. 538 quid agimus? Virg. γ Aen. iii. 88 quem sequimur? The indicative is somewhat more colloquial than the subjunctive.
